msgstr ""
"Tab :guilabel:`Penerima`: tambahkan/hapus pengguna yang menerima email "
"digest. Lihat bagian tentang :ref:`digest-emails/recipients`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/companies/digest_emails.rst:57
msgid ""
