msgid "Turn the printer back on and refresh the page again."
msgstr "Nyalakan kembali printer dan muat ulang halaman lagi."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:200
msgid "Double-check the list again to see if the printer re-appears."
msgstr "Periksa kembali daftar untuk melihat apakah printer muncul kembali."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:201
msgid ""
"The printer that disappeared and reappears again on the listed printers is "
"the name of the printer in question. It can be :guilabel:`Unknown` "
"under :guilabel:`Local printers`."
msgstr ""
"Printer yang hilang dan muncul kembali pada daftar printer adalah nama "
"printer yang dimaksud. Bisa jadi muncul sebagai :guilabel:`Unknown` di "
"bawah :guilabel:`Local printers`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:204
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Add Printer` page, specify the printer's :guilabel:`Name` "
"using the following convention: "
"`<printer_name>__IMC_<param_1>_<param_2>_..._<param_n>__`, where:"
msgstr ""
"Pada halaman :guilabel:`Add Printer`, tentukan :guilabel:`Name` printer "
"menggunakan konvensi berikut: "
"`<printer_name>__IMC_<param_1>_<param_2>_..._<param_n>__`, di mana:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:207
msgid ""
"`printer_name` is the printer's name. It can contain any character except "
"`_`, `/`, `#`, or ` ` (space character)."
msgstr ""
"`printer_name` adalah nama printer. Dapat berisi karakter apa pun kecuali "
"`_`, `/`, `#`, atau ` ` (karakter spasi)."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:209
msgid ""
"`IMC`: This stands for *Image Mode Column* (the simplified name for `ESC *`)."
msgstr ""
"`IMC`: Singkatan dari *Image Mode Column* (nama sederhana untuk `ESC *`)."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:210
msgid "`param_1`: This stands for the specific parameter:"
msgstr "`param_1`: Singkatan dari parameter spesifik:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:212
msgid ""
"`SCALE<X>`: Scale of the picture (with the same aspect ratio). `X` should be "
"an integer describing the scale percentage that should be used. For example, "
"`100` is the original size, `50` is half the size, and `200` is twice the "
"size."
msgstr ""
"`SCALE<X>`: Skala gambar (dengan rasio aspek yang sama). `X` harus berupa "
"bilangan bulat yang menjelaskan persentase skala yang akan digunakan. "
"Misalnya, `100` adalah ukuran asli, `50` adalah setengah ukuran, dan `200` "
"adalah dua kali ukuran."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:215
msgid ""
"`LDV`: *Low Density Vertical* (will be set to *High Density Vertical* if not "
"specified)."
msgstr ""
"`LDV`: *Low Density Vertical* (akan diatur ke *High Density Vertical* jika "
"tidak ditentukan)."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:216
msgid ""
"`LDH`: *Low Density Horizontal* (will be set to *High Density Horizontal* if "
"not specified)."
msgstr ""
"`LDH`: *Low Density Horizontal* (akan diatur ke *High Density Horizontal* "
"jika tidak ditentukan)."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:219
msgid ""
"*Density* parameters might need to be configured in a particular way, "
"depending on the printer model."
msgstr ""
"Parameter *Density* mungkin perlu dikonfigurasi dengan cara tertentu, "
"tergantung pada model printer."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:221
msgid ""
"Refer to `Epson's ESC * documentation <https://download4.epson.biz/sec_pubs/"
"pos/reference_en/escpos/esc_asterisk.html>`_ to determine if the printer "
"requires these parameters to be set."
msgstr ""
"Lihat `dokumentasi ESC * Epson <https://download4.epson.biz/sec_pubs/pos/"
"reference_en/escpos/esc_asterisk.html>`_ untuk menentukan apakah printer "
"memerlukan parameter ini diatur."

