#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:353
msgid "DYMO LabelWriter print issue"
msgstr "Masalah cetak DYMO LabelWriter"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:355
msgid ""
"The DYMO LabelWriter has a known issue in printing with IoT systems. The "
"OpenPrinting CUPS server installs the printer using :guilabel:`Local RAW "
"Printer` drivers. In order to print anything, the correct :guilabel:`Make "
"and Model` needs to be set to reference the correct driver when using the "
"device."
msgstr ""
"DYMO LabelWriter memiliki masalah yang diketahui dalam pencetakan dengan "
"sistem IoT. Server OpenPrinting CUPS menginstal printer menggunakan "
"driver :guilabel:`Local RAW Printer`. Untuk mencetak apa "
"pun, :guilabel:`Make and Model` yang benar perlu diatur untuk mereferensikan "
"driver yang tepat saat menggunakan perangkat."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:360
msgid ""
"Additionally, a new printer needs to be added to reduce the print delay that "
"occurs after updating the driver."
msgstr ""
"Selain itu, printer baru perlu ditambahkan untuk mengurangi penundaan cetak "
"yang terjadi setelah memperbarui driver."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:364
msgid ""
"The DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO printer is the recommended DYMO printer for use "
"with Odoo and IoT systems. This device combines two printers: a label "
"printer and a tape printer. When configuring the following processes, it is "
"essential to select the correct model (either DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO Label "
"(en) or DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO Tape (en)). For consistency, the following "
"processes outline configuration steps for the DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO Label "
"(en) model. Adjust the model selections as needed."
msgstr ""
"Printer DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO adalah printer DYMO yang direkomendasikan "
"untuk digunakan dengan Odoo dan sistem IoT. Perangkat ini menggabungkan dua "
"printer: printer label dan printer pita. Saat mengonfigurasi proses berikut, "
"penting untuk memilih model yang benar (baik DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO Label "
"(en) atau DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO Tape (en)). Untuk konsistensi, proses "
"berikut menguraikan langkah-langkah konfigurasi untuk model DYMO LabelWriter "
"450 DUO Label (en). Sesuaikan pilihan model sesuai kebutuhan."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:374
msgid "DYMO LabelWriter not printing"
msgstr "DYMO LabelWriter tidak mencetak"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:376
msgid "If the DYMO LabelWriter fails to print, install a new driver:"
msgstr "Jika DYMO LabelWriter gagal mencetak, instal driver baru:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:378
#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:414
msgid ""
"Access the IoT system's homepage and click :menuselection:`Printer server` "
"to open the OpenPrinting CUPS console."
msgstr ""
"Akses beranda sistem IoT dan klik :menuselection:`Printer server` untuk "
"membuka konsol OpenPrinting CUPS."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:380
msgid ""
"Click :menuselection:`Printers` in the top menu, then click the printer in "
"the list."
msgstr ""
"Klik :menuselection:`Printers` di menu atas, lalu klik printer dalam daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:381
msgid "Select :guilabel:`Maintenance` in the first dropdown menu."
msgstr "Pilih :guilabel:`Maintenance` di menu dropdown pertama."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:382
msgid "Select :guilabel:`Modify Printer` in the second dropdown menu."
msgstr "Pilih :guilabel:`Modify Printer` di menu dropdown kedua."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:0
msgid ""
"Modify the make and model of the DYMO LabelWriter. Maintenance and Modify "
"dropdown\n"
"menus highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Ubah make dan model DYMO LabelWriter. Menu dropdown Maintenance dan Modify "
"disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:388
msgid ""
"Select the specific network connection/printer on which the modification "
"should be made and click :guilabel:`Continue`."
msgstr ""
"Pilih koneksi jaringan/printer spesifik yang akan dimodifikasi dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Continue`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:390
msgid ""
"On the next page, click :guilabel:`Continue`, then select :guilabel:`DYMO` "
"from the :guilabel:`Make` dropdown list."
msgstr ""
"Pada halaman berikutnya, klik :guilabel:`Continue`, lalu "
"pilih :guilabel:`DYMO` dari daftar dropdown :guilabel:`Make`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:392
msgid ""
"Click on :guilabel:`Continue` and set the :guilabel:`Model` "
"to :guilabel:`DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO Label (en)` (or whichever DYMO "
"printer model is being used)."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Continue` dan atur :guilabel:`Model` ke :guilabel:`DYMO "
"LabelWriter 450 DUO Label (en)` (atau model printer DYMO mana pun yang "
"digunakan)."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:394
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Modify Printer` to set the new driver; a confirmation page "
"appears."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Modify Printer` untuk mengatur driver baru; halaman "
"konfirmasi muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:395
msgid ""
"Click :menuselection:`Printers` in the top menu; all printers installed on "
"the OpenPrinting CUPS server appear, including the newly "
"updated :guilabel:`DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO Label` (or whichever DYMO "
"printer model is being used)."
msgstr ""
"Klik :menuselection:`Printers` di menu atas; semua printer yang diinstal "
"pada server OpenPrinting CUPS muncul, termasuk :guilabel:`DYMO LabelWriter "
"450 DUO Label` yang baru diperbarui (atau model printer DYMO mana pun yang "
"digunakan)."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:398
msgid ""
"Click the newly updated printer, then click the :guilabel:`Maintenance` "
"dropdown menu and select :guilabel:`Print Test Page` to print a test label. "
"The test label is printed after a few seconds if the driver update was "
"successful."
msgstr ""
"Klik printer yang baru diperbarui, lalu klik menu "
"dropdown :guilabel:`Maintenance` dan pilih :guilabel:`Print Test Page` untuk "
"mencetak label uji. Label uji dicetak setelah beberapa detik jika pembaruan "
"driver berhasil."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:402
msgid "To reduce this delay, add a new printer using the steps below."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengurangi penundaan ini, tambahkan printer baru menggunakan langkah-"
"langkah di bawah ini."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:405
msgid "DYMO LabelWriter print delay"
msgstr "Penundaan pencetakan DYMO LabelWriter"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:408
msgid ""
"If the DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO printer is not printing at all, or is not "
"recognized (i.e., it has a :guilabel:`RAW` driver type), then :ref:`update "
"the drivers on the device <printer/dymo/update_drivers>`."
msgstr ""
"Jika printer DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO tidak mencetak sama sekali, atau tidak "
"dikenali (yaitu, memiliki tipe driver :guilabel:`RAW`), maka :ref:`perbarui "
"driver pada perangkat <printer/dymo/update_drivers>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:412
msgid ""
"To resolve the delay issue after modifying the driver, reinstall the printer:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengatasi masalah penundaan setelah memodifikasi driver, instal ulang "
"printer:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:416
msgid ""
"Click :menuselection:`Administration` in the top menu, then "
"click :guilabel:`Add a Printer`."
msgstr ""
"Klik :menuselection:`Administration` di menu atas, lalu klik :guilabel:`Add "
"a Printer`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:417
msgid ""
"On the next page, in the :guilabel:`Local Printers` section, "
"select :guilabel:`DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO Label (DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO "
"Label)` (or whichever DYMO printer model is being used) pre-installed "
"printer. Click :guilabel:`Continue`."
msgstr ""
"Pada halaman berikutnya, di bagian :guilabel:`Local Printers`, pilih printer "
"yang telah terpasang :guilabel:`DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO Label (DYMO "
"LabelWriter 450 DUO Label)` (atau model printer DYMO mana pun yang sedang "
"digunakan). Klik :guilabel:`Continue`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:0
msgid ""
"Add a printer screen on OpenPrinting CUPS with DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO "
"Label\n"
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Layar tambah printer pada OpenPrinting CUPS dengan DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO "
"Label\n"
"disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:425
msgid ""
"On the following screen, update the :guilabel:`Name` to something easily "
"identifiable, as the original printer will remain in the list. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Continue`."
msgstr ""
"Pada layar berikutnya, perbarui :guilabel:`Name` menjadi sesuatu yang mudah "
"diidentifikasi, karena printer asli akan tetap ada dalam daftar. Kemudian, "
"klik :guilabel:`Continue`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:0
msgid ""
"Rename printer page in the 'Add a Printer' flow, with the name field "
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Halaman ganti nama printer dalam alur 'Add a Printer', dengan kolom nama "
"disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:431
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Model` field to :guilabel:`DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO Label "
"(en)` (or whichever DYMO printer model is being used), then "
"click :guilabel:`Add Printer` to complete the installation."
msgstr ""
"Atur kolom :guilabel:`Model` ke :guilabel:`DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO Label "
"(en)` (atau model printer DYMO mana pun yang sedang digunakan), lalu "
"klik :guilabel:`Add Printer` untuk menyelesaikan instalasi."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:0
msgid ""
"Choose model screen on the OpenPrinting CUPS console with model and add a "
"printer\n"
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Layar pilih model pada konsol OpenPrinting CUPS dengan model dan tambah "
"printer\n"
"disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:439
msgid ""
"Click :menuselection:`Printers` in the top menu and click the newly "
"installed printer :guilabel:`DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO Label` (or whichever "
"DYMO printer model is being used) from in the list."
msgstr ""
"Klik :menuselection:`Printers` di menu atas dan klik printer yang baru "
"diinstal :guilabel:`DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO Label` (atau model printer DYMO "
"mana pun yang sedang digunakan) dari daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:0
msgid "Printer page with newly installed printer highlighted."
msgstr "Halaman printer dengan printer yang baru diinstal disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:446
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Maintenance` dropdown list and select :guilabel:`Print "
"Test Page` to print a test label. The test label should print out "
"immediately, or after one or two seconds."
msgstr ""
"Klik daftar dropdown :guilabel:`Maintenance` dan pilih :guilabel:`Print Test "
"Page` untuk mencetak label uji. Label uji seharusnya tercetak segera, atau "
"setelah satu atau dua detik."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:450
msgid "The Zebra printer does not print anything"
msgstr "Printer Zebra tidak mencetak apa pun"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:452
msgid ""
"Zebra printers are quite sensitive to the format of the printed Zebra "
"Programming Language (ZPL) code. If nothing comes out of the printer or "
"blank labels are printed, try changing the format of the report sent to the "
"printer. To do so, activate the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`, go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> User Interface --> Views`, and "
"search for the corresponding template."
msgstr ""
"Printer Zebra cukup sensitif terhadap format kode Zebra Programming Language "
"(ZPL) yang dicetak. Jika tidak ada yang keluar dari printer atau label "
"kosong dicetak, coba ubah format laporan yang dikirim ke printer. Untuk "
"melakukannya, aktifkan :ref:`mode pengembang <developer-mode>`, "
"buka :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> User Interface --> Views`, "
"dan cari template yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:459
msgid ""
"`Zebra's instructions on printing ZPL files <https://"
"supportcommunity.zebra.com/s/article/Print-a-zpl-file-using-the-Generic-Text-"
"Printer>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Instruksi Zebra tentang pencetakan file ZPL <https://"
"supportcommunity.zebra.com/s/article/Print-a-zpl-file-using-the-Generic-Text-"
"Printer>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:463
msgid "Barcode scanner issues"
msgstr "Masalah pemindai barcode"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:466
msgid "The characters read by the barcode scanner do not match the barcode"
msgstr "Karakter yang dibaca oleh pemindai barcode tidak sesuai dengan barcode"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:468
msgid ""
"By default, most barcode scanners are configured in the US QWERTY format. If "
"the barcode scanner uses a different layout, go to :menuselection:`IoT --> "
"Devices` and click the barcode device's card. Then, select the correct "
"language in the :guilabel:`Keyboard Layout` field."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, sebagian besar pemindai barcode dikonfigurasi dalam format "
"US QWERTY. Jika pemindai barcode menggunakan tata letak yang berbeda, "
"buka :menuselection:`IoT --> Devices` dan klik kartu perangkat barcode. "
"Kemudian, pilih bahasa yang benar di kolom :guilabel:`Keyboard Layout`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:473
#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:503
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Keyboard Layout` is language-specific, with available options "
"varying based on the device and the language of the database "
"(e.g., :guilabel:`English (UK)`, :guilabel:`English (US)`, etc.)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Keyboard Layout` bersifat spesifik bahasa, dengan opsi yang "
"tersedia bervariasi berdasarkan perangkat dan bahasa database "
"(misalnya, :guilabel:`English (UK)`, :guilabel:`English (US)`, dll.)."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:478
msgid "Nothing happens when a barcode is scanned"
msgstr "Tidak terjadi apa-apa saat barcode dipindai"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:480
msgid ""
"Make sure the correct device is selected in the :doc:`Point of Sale settings "
"</applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/pos_iot>` (when "
"applicable) and the barcode is configured to send an `ENTER` character "
"(keycode 28) at the end of every barcode."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan perangkat yang benar dipilih di :doc:`pengaturan Point of Sale </"
"applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/pos_iot>` (jika berlaku) "
"dan barcode dikonfigurasi untuk mengirim karakter `ENTER` (keycode 28) di "
"akhir setiap barcode."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:485
msgid "The barcode scanner is detected as a keyboard"
msgstr "Pemindai barcode terdeteksi sebagai keyboard"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:488
msgid ""
"Some barcode scanners are identified as USB keyboards rather than barcode "
"scanners and are not recognized by IoT systems."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa pemindai barcode diidentifikasi sebagai keyboard USB, bukan "
"pemindai barcode, dan tidak dikenali oleh sistem IoT."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:491
msgid ""
"To change the device type manually, go to :menuselection:`IoT --> Devices` "
"and click the barcode device's card. Then, enable :guilabel:`Is scanner`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengubah jenis perangkat secara manual, buka :menuselection:`IoT --> "
"Devices` dan klik kartu perangkat barcode. Kemudian, aktifkan :guilabel:`Is "
"scanner`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:495
msgid "The barcode scanner processes barcode characters individually"
msgstr "Pemindai barcode memproses karakter barcode satu per satu"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:497
msgid ""
"When accessing the mobile version of Odoo from a mobile device or tablet "
"paired with a barcode scanner via the IoT system, the scanner might "
"interpret each character in a barcode as a separate scan. To resolve this, "
"go to :menuselection:`IoT --> Devices` and click the barcode device's card. "
"Then, select the correct language in the :guilabel:`Keyboard Layout` field."
msgstr ""
"Saat mengakses versi mobile Odoo dari perangkat mobile atau tablet yang "
"dipasangkan dengan pemindai barcode melalui sistem IoT, pemindai mungkin "
"menginterpretasikan setiap karakter dalam barcode sebagai pemindaian "
"terpisah. Untuk mengatasi ini, buka :menuselection:`IoT --> Devices` dan "
"klik kartu perangkat barcode. Kemudian, pilih bahasa yang benar di "
"kolom :guilabel:`Keyboard Layout`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:3
msgid "Connect a scale"
msgstr "Menghubungkan timbangan"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:6
msgid ""
"In EU member states, `certification is legally required <https://eur-"
"lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?"
"uri=uriserv%3AOJ.L_.2014.096.01.0107.01.ENG>`_ to use a scale as an "
"integrated device."
msgstr ""
"Di negara anggota UNI Eropa, `sertifikasi diwajibkan secara hukum <https://"
"eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?"
"uri=uriserv%3AOJ.L_.2014.096.01.0107.01.ENG>`_ untuk menggunakan timbangan "
"sebagai perangkat terintegrasi."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:10
msgid ""
"To connect a scale to the IoT system, use a USB cable. In some cases, you "
"may need a serial-to-USB adapter to complete the connection. If the scale is "
"`compatible with an IoT system <https://www.odoo.com/page/iot-hardware>`_, "
"no additional setup is required; the scale is automatically detected as soon "
"as it is connected. If the scale is not detected, reboot the IoT box "
"or :ref:`restart the Windows virtual IoT service <iot/windows_iot/restart>` "
"and :ref:`update the scale's drivers <iot_updating_iot/handlers>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghubungkan timbangan ke sistem IoT, gunakan kabel USB. Dalam "
"beberapa kasus, Anda mungkin memerlukan adaptor serial-ke-USB untuk "
"menyelesaikan koneksi. Jika timbangan `kompatibel dengan sistem IoT <https://"
"www.odoo.com/page/iot-hardware>`_, tidak diperlukan pengaturan tambahan; "
"timbangan secara otomatis terdeteksi segera setelah terhubung. Jika "
"timbangan tidak terdeteksi, reboot box IoT atau :ref:`restart layanan "
"virtual IoT Windows <iot/windows_iot/restart>` dan :ref:`perbarui driver "
"timbangan <iot_updating_iot/handlers>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:18
msgid ""
"If the scale still does not function after updating the drivers, it might "
"not be `compatible with the Odoo IoT system <https://www.odoo.com/page/iot-"
"hardware>`_. In such cases, a different scale must be used."
msgstr ""
"Jika timbangan masih tidak berfungsi setelah memperbarui driver, kemungkinan "
"tidak `kompatibel dengan sistem Odoo IoT <https://www.odoo.com/page/iot-"
"hardware>`_. Dalam kasus seperti ini, timbangan yang berbeda harus digunakan."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:22
msgid ""
"Once the scale is connected to the IoT system, :doc:`configure it in the POS "
"settings </applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/scale>`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah timbangan terhubung ke sistem IoT, :doc:`konfigurasikan di "
"pengaturan POS </applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/scale>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:26
msgid ""
":doc:`Connect an IoT system to a POS </applications/sales/point_of_sale/"
"hardware_network/pos_iot>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Hubungkan sistem IoT ke POS </applications/sales/point_of_sale/"
"hardware_network/pos_iot>`"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:30
msgid "Ariva S scales"
msgstr "Timbangan Ariva S"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:32
msgid ""
"For Ariva S series scales (manufactured by Mettler-Toledo, LLC.) to function "
"with IoT systems, a specific setting must be modified, and a dedicated "
"Mettler USB-to-proprietary RJ45 cable is required."
msgstr ""
"Agar timbangan seri Ariva S (diproduksi oleh Mettler-Toledo, LLC.) berfungsi "
"dengan sistem IoT, pengaturan tertentu harus diubah, dan kabel khusus "
"Mettler USB-ke-RJ45 proprietary diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:36
msgid ""
"The official Mettler USB-to-RJ45 cable (Mettler part number 72256236) must "
"be used. Contact Mettler or a partner to purchase an authentic cable. **No "
"other** cable works for this configuration."
msgstr ""
"Kabel resmi Mettler USB-ke-RJ45 (nomor bagian Mettler 72256236) harus "
"digunakan. Hubungi Mettler atau mitra untuk membeli kabel asli. **Tidak "
"ada** kabel lain yang berfungsi untuk konfigurasi ini."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:40
msgid ""
"To configure the Ariva S scale for IoT system recognition, refer to page 17 "
"of `Mettler's Setup Guide for Ariva S series scales <https://www.mt.com/dam/"
"RET_DOCS/Ariv.pdf>`_ and follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi timbangan Ariva S agar dikenali sistem IoT, lihat "
"halaman 17 dari `Panduan Setup Mettler untuk timbangan seri Ariva S <https://"
"www.mt.com/dam/RET_DOCS/Ariv.pdf>`_ dan ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:43
msgid ""
"Hold the **>T<** button for eight seconds, or until :guilabel:`CONF` appears."
msgstr ""
"Tahan tombol **>T<** selama delapan detik, atau hingga :guilabel:`CONF` "
"muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:44
msgid ""
"Press **>T<** until :guilabel:`GRP 3` appears, then press **>0<** to confirm."
msgstr ""
"Tekan **>T<** hingga :guilabel:`GRP 3` muncul, kemudian tekan **>0<** untuk "
"mengonfirmasi."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:45
msgid ""
"At step :guilabel:`3.1`, make sure the value is set to :guilabel:`1` (USB "
"Virtual COM ports) by pressing **>T<** to cycle through the options."
msgstr ""
"Pada langkah :guilabel:`3.1`, pastikan nilainya diatur ke :guilabel:`1` (USB "
"Virtual COM ports) dengan menekan **>T<** untuk beralih melalui opsi."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:47
msgid ""
"Press **>0<** until :guilabel:`3.6` (if available, otherwise skip the next "
"step)."
msgstr ""
"Tekan **>0<** hingga :guilabel:`3.6` (jika tersedia, jika tidak lewati "
"langkah berikutnya)."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:48
msgid ""
"At step :guilabel:`3.6`, make sure the value is set to :guilabel:`3` (8217 "
"Mettler-Toledo (WO)) by pressing **>T<** to cycle through the options."
msgstr ""
"Pada langkah :guilabel:`3.6`, pastikan nilainya diatur ke :guilabel:`3` "
"(8217 Mettler-Toledo (WO)) dengan menekan **>T<** untuk beralih melalui opsi."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:50
msgid ""
"Press **>0<** (multiple times if necessary) until :guilabel:`GRP 4` appears."
msgstr ""
"Tekan **>0<** (beberapa kali jika perlu) hingga :guilabel:`GRP 4` muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:51
msgid "Press **>T<** until :guilabel:`EXIT` appears."
msgstr "Tekan **>T<** hingga :guilabel:`EXIT` muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:54
msgid "Do **not** make any other changes unless otherwise needed."
msgstr "**Jangan** melakukan perubahan lain kecuali diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:56
msgid "Press **>0<**."
msgstr "Tekan **>0<**."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:57
msgid "Press **>0<** again to :guilabel:`SAVE`; the scale restarts."
msgstr "Tekan **>0<** lagi untuk :guilabel:`SAVE`; timbangan akan restart."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/scale.rst:58
msgid ""
"Reboot the IoT box or :ref:`restart the Windows virtual IoT service <iot/"
"windows_iot/restart>`. The scale should then appear as `Toledo 8217`."
msgstr ""
"Reboot IoT box atau :ref:`restart layanan virtual IoT Windows <iot/"
"windows_iot/restart>`. Timbangan kemudian akan muncul sebagai `Toledo 8217`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/screen.rst:3
msgid "Connect a screen"
msgstr "Hubungkan layar"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/screen.rst:5
msgid ""
"The :doc:`IoT box <../iot_box>` can be connected to a screen, e.g. to ease "
"the IoT box's setup and/or serve as a :doc:`customer display </applications/"
"sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/customer_display>` to show customers "
"their :doc:`Point of Sale </applications/sales/point_of_sale>` orders."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Kotak IoT <../iot_box>` dapat dihubungkan ke layar, misalnya untuk "
"mempermudah pengaturan kotak IoT dan/atau berfungsi sebagai :doc:`tampilan "
"pelanggan </applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/"
"customer_display>` untuk menampilkan pesanan :doc:`POS </applications/sales/"
"point_of_sale>` kepada pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/screen.rst:13
msgid ""
"Connect the screen to the IoT box using a micro-HDMI cable. If the "
"connection was successful, the external monitor displays "
"the :guilabel:`Status display` screen."
msgstr ""
"Hubungkan layar ke IoT box menggunakan kabel micro-HDMI. Jika koneksi "
"berhasil, monitor eksternal menampilkan layar :guilabel:`Status display`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/screen.rst:None
msgid "Default Status Display screen"
msgstr "Layar Status Display default"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/screen.rst:19
msgid "The screen also appears in the IoT box's list of devices:"
msgstr "Layar juga muncul dalam daftar perangkat IoT box:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/screen.rst:21
msgid "on the :ref:`IoT box's form <iot/connect/IoT-form>`;"
msgstr "pada :ref:`formulir IoT box <iot/connect/IoT-form>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/screen.rst:22
msgid "on the :ref:`IoT box's homepage <iot/iot-box/homepage>`;"
msgstr "pada :ref:`homepage IoT box <iot/iot-box/homepage>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/screen.rst:23
msgid "in the IoT app, under the menu :menuselection:`IoT --> Devices`."
msgstr "di aplikasi IoT, di bawah menu :menuselection:`IoT --> Devices`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/screen.rst:26
msgid ""
"To use the screen as a :doc:`customer display </applications/sales/"
"point_of_sale/hardware_network/customer_display>` in the "
"POS, :ref:`configure the POS accordingly <pos/hardware_network/display-"
"configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan layar sebagai :doc:`tampilan pelanggan </applications/"
"sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/customer_display>` di "
"POS, :ref:`konfigurasikan POS sesuai dengan itu <pos/hardware_network/"
"display-configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/screen.rst:29
msgid ""
"To display a specific website on the screen instead of the POS customer "
"display, go to :menuselection:`IoT --> Devices`, click the screen's card, "
"then enter the desired website's URL in the :guilabel:`Display URL` field."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menampilkan website tertentu pada layar alih-alih tampilan pelanggan "
"POS, buka :menuselection:`IoT --> Devices`, klik kartu layar, lalu masukkan "
"URL website yang diinginkan di kolom :guilabel:`Display URL`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced.rst:5
msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "Lanjutan"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/ssh_connect.rst:3
msgid "IoT box SSH connection"
msgstr "Koneksi SSH IoT box"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/ssh_connect.rst:6
msgid ""
"SSH connections are only available for :doc:`IoT boxes <../iot_box>`, not "
"the :doc:`Windows virtual IoT <../windows_iot>`."
msgstr ""
"Koneksi SSH hanya tersedia untuk :doc:`IoT box <../iot_box>`, bukan "
"untuk :doc:`Windows virtual IoT <../windows_iot>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/ssh_connect.rst:10
msgid ""
"This feature should **only** be used with trusted parties, as it provides "
"administrative access to the IoT box, which can create security issues."
msgstr ""
"Fitur ini **hanya** boleh digunakan dengan pihak yang dipercaya, karena "
"memberikan akses administratif ke IoT box yang dapat menimbulkan masalah "
"keamanan."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/ssh_connect.rst:12
msgid ""
"Managing an SSH connection is **not** covered under the standard Odoo "
"support scope. Visit the `Odoo Support <https://www.odoo.com/help>`_ page "
"for additional information about what is covered."
msgstr ""
"Mengelola koneksi SSH **tidak** tercakup dalam cakupan dukungan standar "
"Odoo. Kunjungi halaman `Dukungan Odoo <https://www.odoo.com/help>`_ untuk "
"informasi tambahan tentang apa yang tercakup."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/ssh_connect.rst:16
msgid ""
"To provide an :abbr:`SSH (secure shell protocol)` connection to an IoT box, "
"you must generate a password:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyediakan koneksi :abbr:`SSH (secure shell protocol)` ke IoT box, "
"Anda harus membuat password:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/ssh_connect.rst:19
msgid ""
"Open the IoT app, click the relevant IoT box's card, and "
"click :guilabel:`Homepage`."
msgstr ""
"Buka aplikasi IoT, klik kartu IoT box yang relevan, dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Homepage`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/ssh_connect.rst:20
msgid ""
"On the IoT system's homepage, click the :icon:`fa-cogs` (:guilabel:`cogs`) "
"button at the top-right, then :guilabel:`Remote Debug`."
msgstr ""
"Pada homepage sistem IoT, klik tombol :icon:`fa-cogs` (:guilabel:`cogs`) di "
"kanan atas, lalu :guilabel:`Remote Debug`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/ssh_connect.rst:22
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Remote Debugging` popup that opens, "
"click :guilabel:`Generate` and save the password securely. Once you close "
"the popup, the password will no longer be available."
msgstr ""
"Di popup :guilabel:`Remote Debugging` yang terbuka, "
"klik :guilabel:`Generate` dan simpan password dengan aman. Setelah Anda "
"menutup popup, password tidak akan tersedia lagi."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/ssh_connect.rst:0
#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:None
