#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:9
msgid "The pairing code does not appear or does not work"
msgstr "Kode pemasangan tidak muncul atau tidak berfungsi"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:11
msgid ""
"The :ref:`pairing code <iot/connect/pairing-code>` might not be displayed or "
"printed under the following circumstances:"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Kode pemasangan <iot/connect/pairing-code>` mungkin tidak ditampilkan "
"atau dicetak dalam keadaan berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:14
msgid "The IoT system is not connected to the network."
msgstr "Sistem IoT tidak terhubung ke jaringan."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:15
msgid ""
"The IoT system is already connected to an Odoo database. :ref:`Disconnect it "
"from the database <iot/connect/disconnect>`."
msgstr ""
"Sistem IoT sudah terhubung ke database Odoo. :ref:`Putuskan koneksi dari "
"database <iot/connect/disconnect>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:17
msgid ""
"The :ref:`pairing code <iot/connect/pairing-code>` display time has expired. "
"Restart the :ref:`IoT box <iot/iot-box/restart>` or the :ref:`Windows "
"virtual IoT service <iot/windows_iot/restart>` to generate and display the "
"pairing code."
msgstr ""
"Waktu tampilan :ref:`kode pemasangan <iot/connect/pairing-code>` telah "
"kedaluwarsa. Restart :ref:`IoT box <iot/iot-box/restart>` atau :ref:`layanan "
"IoT virtual Windows <iot/windows_iot/restart>` untuk menghasilkan dan "
"menampilkan kode pemasangan."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:22
msgid "The IoT system does not connect to the database"
msgstr "Sistem IoT tidak terhubung ke database"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:24
msgid ""
"The IoT system might take a few minutes to restart when it connects to a "
"database. If it still does not appear after a few minutes:"
msgstr ""
"Sistem IoT mungkin memerlukan beberapa menit untuk memulai ulang saat "
"terhubung ke database. Jika masih tidak muncul setelah beberapa menit:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:27
msgid ""
"Verify that the IoT system can reach the database and the server does not "
"use a multi-database environment."
msgstr ""
"Verifikasi bahwa sistem IoT dapat menjangkau database dan server tidak "
"menggunakan lingkungan multi-database."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:29
#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:47
msgid ""
"Restart the :ref:`IoT box <iot/iot-box/restart>` or the :ref:`Windows "
"virtual IoT service <iot/windows_iot/restart>`."
msgstr ""
"Restart :ref:`IoT box <iot/iot-box/restart>` atau :ref:`layanan IoT virtual "
"Windows <iot/windows_iot/restart>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:33
msgid "The IoT system is connected to the Odoo database but cannot be reached"
msgstr "Sistem IoT terhubung ke database Odoo tetapi tidak dapat dijangkau"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:35
msgid ""
"Verify that the IoT system and the computer running the Odoo database are "
"connected to the same network and :ref:`update the DNS settings <iot/"
"troubleshooting/dns>` if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Verifikasi bahwa sistem IoT dan komputer yang menjalankan database Odoo "
"terhubung ke jaringan yang sama dan :ref:`perbarui pengaturan DNS <iot/"
"troubleshooting/dns>` jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:39
msgid ""
"The Windows virtual IoT's homepage cannot be accessed from another device"
msgstr "Beranda Windows virtual IoT tidak dapat diakses dari perangkat lain"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:41
msgid ""
"Ensure the device is connected to the same network as the Windows virtual "
"IoT."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan perangkat terhubung ke jaringan yang sama dengan IoT virtual "
"Windows."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:42
msgid "Check the :ref:`iot/windows-iot/firewall`."
msgstr "Periksa :ref:`iot/windows-iot/firewall`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:45
msgid "The IoT system does not work after an Odoo upgrade"
msgstr "Sistem IoT tidak berfungsi setelah upgrade Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:50
msgid ""
"If the issue persists, :ref:`update its image <iot/updating_iot/image-code>` "
"by flashing the IoT box's card or :ref:`uninstalling the Windows virtual IoT "
"program <iot/windows_iot/uninstall>` and :ref:`reinstalling the virtual IoT "
"package <iot/windows-iot/installation>`."
msgstr ""
"Jika masalah berlanjut, :ref:`perbarui imagenya <iot/updating_iot/image-"
"code>` dengan melakukan flash pada kartu IoT box atau :ref:`uninstall "
"program IoT virtual Windows <iot/windows_iot/uninstall>` dan :ref:`install "
"ulang paket IoT virtual <iot/windows-iot/installation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:57
msgid ""
"The IoT system's homepage can be accessed using its IP address but not the "
"`xxx.odoo-iot.com` URL"
msgstr ""
"Halaman utama sistem IoT dapat diakses menggunakan alamat IP tetapi tidak "
"menggunakan URL `xxx.odoo-iot.com`"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:59
msgid ""
"Contact your system or network administrator to address the issue. Network-"
"related problems are beyond the scope of Odoo support services."
msgstr ""
"Hubungi administrator sistem atau jaringan Anda untuk mengatasi masalah ini. "
"Masalah terkait jaringan berada di luar cakupan layanan dukungan Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:62
msgid ""
"If the router allows manual :abbr:`DNS (Domain Name System)` configuration, "
"update the settings to use `Google DNS <https://developers.google.com/speed/"
"public-dns>`_."
msgstr ""
"Jika router memungkinkan konfigurasi :abbr:`DNS (Domain Name System)` "
"manual, perbarui pengaturan untuk menggunakan `Google DNS <https://"
"developers.google.com/speed/public-dns>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:64
msgid ""
"If the router does not support this, you need to update the DNS settings "
"directly on each device that interacts with the IoT system to use `Google "
"DNS <https://developers.google.com/speed/public-dns>`_. Instructions for "
"configuring DNS on individual devices can be found on the respective "
"manufacturer's website."
msgstr ""
"Jika router tidak mendukung ini, Anda perlu memperbarui pengaturan DNS "
"secara langsung pada setiap perangkat yang berinteraksi dengan sistem IoT "
"untuk menggunakan `Google DNS <https://developers.google.com/speed/public-"
"dns>`_. Instruksi untuk mengonfigurasi DNS pada perangkat individual dapat "
"ditemukan di situs web produsen masing-masing."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:70
msgid ""
"Some IoT devices, such as payment terminals, likely do not require DNS "
"changes, as they are typically pre-configured with custom DNS settings."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa perangkat IoT, seperti terminal pembayaran, kemungkinan tidak "
"memerlukan perubahan DNS, karena biasanya sudah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya "
"dengan pengaturan DNS khusus."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:72
msgid ""
"On some browsers, an error code mentioning the DNS (such as "
"`DNS_PROBE_FINISHED_NXDOMAIN`) is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Pada beberapa browser, kode error yang menyebutkan DNS (seperti "
"`DNS_PROBE_FINISHED_NXDOMAIN`) ditampilkan."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:78
msgid "HTTPS certificate generation issues and errors"
msgstr "Masalah dan error pembuatan sertifikat HTTPS"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:81
msgid "The HTTPS certificate does not generate"
msgstr "Sertifikat HTTPS tidak dibuat"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:83
msgid "Potential causes include the following:"
msgstr "Penyebab potensial meliputi hal-hal berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:85
msgid ""
"The database doesn't meet the :ref:`eligibility requirements <iot/"
"https_certificate_iot/iot-eligibility>` for generating an :ref:`HTTPS "
"certificate <iot/connect/https_certificate>`."
msgstr ""
"Database tidak memenuhi :ref:`persyaratan kelayakan <iot/"
"https_certificate_iot/iot-eligibility>` untuk menghasilkan :ref:`sertifikat "
"HTTPS <iot/connect/https_certificate>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:88
msgid ""
"The firewall is preventing the HTTPS certificate from generating correctly. "
"In this case, deactivate the firewall until the certificate is successfully "
"generated."
msgstr ""
"Firewall mencegah sertifikat HTTPS dibuat dengan benar. Dalam hal ini, "
"nonaktifkan firewall hingga sertifikat berhasil dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:92
msgid ""
"Some devices, such as routers with a built-in firewall, can prevent the "
"HTTPS certificate from generating."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa perangkat, seperti router dengan firewall bawaan, dapat mencegah "
"sertifikat HTTPS dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:96
msgid "Errors"
msgstr "Error"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:98
msgid ""
"A specific error code is displayed on the IoT system's homepage if any "
"issues occur during the generation or reception of the :ref:`HTTPS "
"certificate <iot/connect/https_certificate>`."
msgstr ""
"Kode kesalahan tertentu ditampilkan pada beranda sistem IoT jika terjadi "
"masalah selama pembuatan atau penerimaan :ref:`sertifikat HTTPS <iot/connect/"
"https_certificate>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:102
msgid ""
"When you access the IoT system's homepage, it automatically checks for an "
"HTTPS certificate and attempts to generate one if it is missing. If an error "
"appears, refresh the page to see if the issue is resolved."
msgstr ""
"Saat Anda mengakses halaman beranda sistem IoT, secara otomatis dilakukan "
"pemeriksaan sertifikat HTTPS dan upaya untuk menghasilkannya jika tidak ada. "
"Jika muncul error, muat ulang halaman untuk melihat apakah masalah tersebut "
"teratasi."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:107
msgid "Missing credentials"
msgstr "Kredensial tidak ada"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:109
msgid ""
"The contract and/or database :abbr:`UUID (Universal Unique Identifier)` is "
"missing from the IoT."
msgstr ""
"Kontrak dan/atau database :abbr:`UUID (Universal Unique Identifier)` tidak "
"ditemukan dari IoT."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:111
msgid ""
"Verify that both values are correctly configured. To update "
"them, :ref:`access the IoT box's <iot/iot-box/homepage>` or :ref:`Windows "
"virtual IoT's homepage <iot/windows-iot/homepage>`, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cogs` (:guilabel:`cogs`) button, then click :guilabel:`Credentials`."
msgstr ""
"Verifikasi bahwa kedua nilai dikonfigurasi dengan benar. Untuk "
"memperbaruinya, :ref:`akses homepage IoT box <iot/iot-box/homepage>` "
"atau :ref:`homepage IoT virtual Windows <iot/windows-iot/homepage>`, klik "
"tombol :icon:`fa-cogs` (:guilabel:`roda gigi`), lalu "
"klik :guilabel:`Credentials`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:116
msgid ""
"To access the full request exception details with information regarding the "
"error, :ref:`enable the developer mode <developer-mode>`, click the IoT "
"system's card in the IoT app, and click :guilabel:`Download logs` on "
"the :ref:`IoT system's form <iot/connect/IoT-form>`. To define the log "
"levels recorded in the IoT system's log file, :ref:`access the IoT box's "
"<iot/windows-iot/homepage>` or :ref:`Windows virtual IoT's <iot/iot-box/"
"homepage>` homepage, click the :icon:`fa-cogs` (:guilabel:`cogs`) button, "
"then :guilabel:`Log level` at the bottom of the page."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses detail exception permintaan lengkap dengan informasi terkait "
"error, :ref:`aktifkan mode pengembang <developer-mode>`, klik kartu sistem "
"IoT di aplikasi IoT, dan klik :guilabel:`Download logs` pada :ref:`formulir "
"sistem IoT <iot/connect/IoT-form>`. Untuk menentukan level log yang dicatat "
"dalam file log sistem IoT, :ref:`akses halaman beranda IoT box <iot/windows-"
"iot/homepage>` atau :ref:`Windows virtual IoT <iot/iot-box/homepage>`, klik "
"tombol :icon:`fa-cogs` (:guilabel:`cogs`), kemudian :guilabel:`Log level` di "
"bagian bawah halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:123
msgid ""
"To address network-related issues, contact your system or network "
"administrator; these issues are beyond the scope of Odoo support services."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengatasi masalah terkait jaringan, hubungi administrator sistem atau "
"jaringan Anda; masalah ini berada di luar cakupan layanan dukungan Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:127
msgid "Odoo.com not reachable"
msgstr "Odoo.com tidak dapat dijangkau"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:129
msgid ""
"The IoT system successfully reached `<https://www.odoo.com>`_ but received "
"an unexpected `HTTP response (status codes) <https://developer.mozilla.org/"
"en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Status>`_."
msgstr ""
"Sistem IoT berhasil menjangkau `<https://www.odoo.com>`_ tetapi menerima "
"`respons HTTP (kode status) <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/"
"HTTP/Status>`_ yang tidak terduga."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:132
msgid "To solve this issue:"
msgstr "Untuk mengatasi masalah ini:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:134
msgid ""
"Open `<https://www.odoo.com>`_ in a web browser to check if the website is "
"temporarily down for maintenance."
msgstr ""
"Buka `<https://www.odoo.com>`_ di browser web untuk memeriksa apakah situs "
"web sedang down sementara untuk pemeliharaan."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:0
msgid ""
"If `<https://www.odoo.com>`_ is down for maintenance, wait for it to resume."
msgstr ""
"Jika `<https://www.odoo.com>`_ sedang down untuk pemeliharaan, tunggu hingga "
"kembali aktif."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:0
msgid ""
"If the website is operational, open a `support ticket <https://www.odoo.com/"
"help>`_ and make sure to include the 3-digit HTTPS status code in the ticket."
msgstr ""
"Jika situs web beroperasi, buka `tiket dukungan <https://www.odoo.com/"
"help>`_ dan pastikan untuk menyertakan kode status HTTPS 3 digit dalam tiket."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:141
msgid "Still no certificate?"
msgstr "Masih belum ada sertifikat?"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:143
msgid ""
"If the IoT system successfully connected to `<https://www.odoo.com>`_, but "
"the server refused to provide the :ref:`HTTPS certificate <iot/connect/"
"https_certificate>`."
msgstr ""
"Jika sistem IoT berhasil terhubung ke `<https://www.odoo.com>`_, tetapi "
"server menolak untuk menyediakan :ref:`sertifikat HTTPS <iot/connect/"
"https_certificate>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:146
msgid ""
"Check that the IoT system and database meet the :ref:`eligibility "
"requirements <iot/https_certificate_iot/iot-eligibility>` for an HTTPS "
"certificate."
msgstr ""
"Periksa bahwa sistem IoT dan database memenuhi :ref:`persyaratan kelayakan "
"<iot/https_certificate_iot/iot-eligibility>` untuk sertifikat HTTPS."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:150
msgid "Grant Odoo support team access to an IoT Box"
msgstr "Berikan akses tim dukungan Odoo ke IoT Box"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:152
msgid ""
"If you need to grant remote access to an IoT Box, you can provide a "
"Tailscale token on the IoT Box's homepage. This allows the Odoo support team "
"to access the IoT Box for troubleshooting securely."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda perlu memberikan akses jarak jauh ke IoT Box, Anda dapat "
"menyediakan token Tailscale pada beranda IoT Box. Ini memungkinkan tim "
"dukungan Odoo mengakses IoT Box untuk pemecahan masalah dengan aman."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:157
msgid ""
"Only enter a token from a trusted source, such as an official Odoo support "
"representative. Providing a token grants access to the IoT Box and your "
"entire local network, so it should be done with caution."
msgstr ""
"Hanya masukkan token dari sumber tepercaya, seperti perwakilan dukungan Odoo "
"resmi. Memberikan token akan memberikan akses ke IoT Box dan seluruh "
"jaringan lokal Anda, jadi harus dilakukan dengan hati-hati."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:161
msgid ""
"On the :ref:`IoT Box's homepage <iot/iot-box/homepage>`, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cogs` (:guilabel:`cogs`) button, then click :guilabel:`Debugging Tools`. In "
"the pop-up window, enter the Tailscale token provided by the Odoo support "
"team and click :guilabel:`Enable`."
msgstr ""
"Pada :ref:`beranda IoT Box <iot/iot-box/homepage>`, klik tombol :icon:`fa-"
"cogs` (:guilabel:`roda gigi`), lalu klik :guilabel:`Debugging Tools`. Pada "
"jendela pop-up, masukkan token Tailscale yang disediakan oleh tim dukungan "
"Odoo dan klik :guilabel:`Enable`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:166
msgid ""
"**Remote Debug** is only available for :doc:`IoT boxes <../iot_box>`, not "
"the :doc:`Windows virtual IoT <../windows_iot>`."
msgstr ""
"**Remote Debug** hanya tersedia untuk :doc:`kotak IoT <../iot_box>`, bukan "
":doc:`Windows virtual IoT <../windows_iot>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:170
msgid "Is the IoT Box down?"
msgstr "Apakah IoT Box mati?"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:172
msgid ""
"If the IoT Box is down, you can still enable remote access for the Odoo "
"support team. Just provide the key in the only field displayed on "
"the :ref:`homepage <iot/iot-box/homepage>` and click :guilabel:`Enable`."
msgstr ""
"Jika IoT Box mati, Anda masih dapat mengaktifkan akses jarak jauh untuk tim "
"dukungan Odoo. Cukup berikan kunci di satu-satunya kolom yang ditampilkan "
"pada :ref:`beranda <iot/iot-box/homepage>` dan klik :guilabel:`Enable`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:180
msgid ""
"Enabling remote access on a down IoT Box is only available from version "
"above v26.01.2026. If your IoT Box doesn't have this option, you will need "
"to :ref:`flash the IoT Box's card with the latest image <iot/updating_iot/"
"image-code>`."
msgstr ""
"Mengaktifkan akses jarak jauh pada IoT Box yang mati hanya tersedia dari "
"versi di atas v26.01.2026. Jika IoT Box Anda tidak memiliki opsi ini, Anda "
"perlu :ref:`flash kartu IoT Box dengan image terbaru <iot/updating_iot/image-"
"code>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:5
msgid ""
"Due to the complexity of IoT systems, the term *updating* can refer to "
"several processes, including:"
msgstr ""
"Karena kompleksitas sistem IoT, istilah *memperbarui* dapat merujuk pada "
"beberapa proses, termasuk:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:7
msgid ""
":ref:`Updating the IoT system's image and/or core code <iot/updating_iot/"
"image-code>`;"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Memperbarui image dan/atau kode inti sistem IoT <iot/updating_iot/"
"image-code>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:8
msgid ""
":ref:`Updating the handlers <iot_updating_iot/handlers>`, which include the "
"interfaces and drivers."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Memperbarui handler <iot_updating_iot/handlers>`, yang mencakup "
"antarmuka dan driver."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:13
msgid "Image and core code update"
msgstr "Pembaruan image dan kode inti"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:19
msgid ""
"To check if the IoT box is up-to-date (and update it if "
"needed), :ref:`access the IoT box's homepage <iot/iot-box/homepage>`, click "
"the :icon:`fa-cogs` (:guilabel:`cogs`) button at the top-right, "
"then :guilabel:`Update` in the :guilabel:`Version` section."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memeriksa apakah IoT box sudah terbaru (dan memperbaruinya jika "
"diperlukan), :ref:`akses halaman beranda IoT box <iot/iot-box/homepage>`, "
"klik tombol :icon:`fa-cogs` (:guilabel:`cogs`) di pojok kanan atas, "
"lalu :guilabel:`Update` di bagian :guilabel:`Version`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:24
msgid ""
":ref:`Enable the developer mode <developer-mode>` to view the current "
"versions of the IoT box's image and core code."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Aktifkan mode pengembang <developer-mode>` untuk melihat versi saat "
"ini dari image dan kode inti IoT box."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:27
msgid "**Image update**"
msgstr "**Pembaruan image**"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:29
msgid ""
"To update the IoT box's image, flash its SD card. Flashing can be performed "
"using `balenaEtcher <https://etcher.balena.io>`_, a free and open-source "
"tool for writing disk images to SD cards."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memperbarui image IoT box, flash kartu SD-nya. Flashing dapat "
"dilakukan menggunakan `balenaEtcher <https://etcher.balena.io>`_, alat "
"gratis dan open-source untuk menulis disk image ke kartu SD."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:34
msgid ""
"Updating the IoT system's image is often required after upgrading the Odoo "
"database to a newer version."
msgstr ""
"Memperbarui image sistem IoT sering diperlukan setelah mengupgrade database "
"Odoo ke versi yang lebih baru."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:36
msgid ""
"A computer with a micro SD card reader/adapter is required to flash the "
"micro SD card."
msgstr ""
"Komputer dengan pembaca/adapter kartu micro SD diperlukan untuk melakukan "
"flash kartu micro SD."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:37
msgid ""
"An alternative software for flashing the micro SD card is `Raspberry Pi "
"Imager <https://www.raspberrypi.com/software/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Perangkat lunak alternatif untuk melakukan flash kartu micro SD adalah "
"`Raspberry Pi Imager <https://www.raspberrypi.com/software/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:40
msgid "`Download balenaEtcher. <https://etcher.balena.io/#download-etcher>`_"
msgstr "`Unduh balenaEtcher. <https://etcher.balena.io/#download-etcher>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:41
msgid "Insert the IoT box's micro SD card into the computer or adapter."
msgstr "Masukkan kartu micro SD IoT box ke dalam komputer atau adapter."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:0
msgid ""
"Open balenaEtcher, click :guilabel:`Flash from URL`, and enter the following "
"URL:"
msgstr ""
"Buka balenaEtcher, klik :guilabel:`Flash from URL`, dan masukkan URL berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:0
msgid "`http://nightly.odoo.com/master/iotbox/iotbox-latest.zip`."
msgstr "`http://nightly.odoo.com/master/iotbox/iotbox-latest.zip`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:44
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Select target` and select the SD card."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Select target` dan pilih kartu SD."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:45
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Flash` and wait for the process to finish."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Flash` dan tunggu hingga proses selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:0
msgid "Flashing the SD card with balenaEtcher"
msgstr "Melakukan flash kartu SD dengan balenaEtcher"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:50
msgid "**Core code update**"
msgstr "**Pembaruan kode inti**"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:52
msgid ""
"To update the IoT box's core code, click :guilabel:`Update` "
"under :guilabel:`IoT Box Update` in the :guilabel:`Update` popup."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memperbarui kode inti IoT box, klik :guilabel:`Update` di "
"bawah :guilabel:`IoT Box Update` dalam popup :guilabel:`Update`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:56
msgid ""
"**Do not turn off or unplug the IoT box** during the update process, as "
"doing so could leave the device in an inconsistent state, requiring the IoT "
"box to be reflashed with a new image."
msgstr ""
"**Jangan matikan atau cabut IoT box** selama proses update, karena hal "
"tersebut dapat menyebabkan perangkat berada dalam kondisi tidak konsisten, "
"yang mengharuskan IoT box di-flash ulang dengan image baru."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:61
msgid ""
"To update the Windows virtual IoT's image and code, :ref:`uninstall the "
"program <iot/windows_iot/uninstall>` and :ref:`reinstall <iot/windows-iot/"
"installation>` the latest package."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memperbarui image dan kode Windows virtual IoT, :ref:`uninstall "
"program <iot/windows_iot/uninstall>` dan :ref:`reinstall <iot/windows-iot/"
"installation>` paket terbaru."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/updating_iot.rst:68
msgid "Handler (driver) update"
msgstr "Pembaruan handler (driver)"

